Ukuze ube neengcamango ezilungileyo zeHong Kong, shiya esi siqithi siye echibini lamanzi aseKowloon.
Inkoliso yophuhliso lwase Hong Kong Island ibizele kwilizwe elisandula kubuyiswa nakunxweme olusemantla.
Le ndawo ayithatha njengendawo yabo abenzi beekoloni zaseBritane ngoko ukuba ufuna ukubona ubungqina bexesha elidlulileyo lobukoloni basekuhlaleni, le yindawo efanelekileyo onokuqalisa kuyo.
Akukho ntsingiselo ekhoyo yokuba le mveliso eyenziweyo yayikukudala. Imibutho yerhafu ichaza izinto esele zigqithiselwe yiminyaka eyi-100 njengamaxabiso.
Inkcazelo ineyantlukwano yendawo, apho umlinganiselo omdala unokufutshane kwimimandla enjengaseMntla Melika kunaseYurophu.
Iimveliso zezandla zinokuthi zichazwe njengezinto zakudala, nangona zincinci kunempahla efanaya ziveliswa ngobuninzi.
Sekunjalo, ipeneli yaba ngumhlobo wabantu abaninzi olungileyo xa ivela.
Ngokudabukisayo, njengoko iindlela zokubhala ezintsha zivelile, ipeneli inikwe imeko kunye nomsebenzi wophando.
Abantu ngoku babhala imiyalezo kwiskrini seekhompyutha, bangasadingi ukusondela kumatshini wokucija iipensela.
Umntu unokuzibuza ukuba kuza kwenzeka ntoni ngekhibhodi xa kufika into entsha.
Uphando lwangekhulu lamashumi amabini eminyaka lubonise ukuba kukho amacandelo amabini okuhluka: okufihliweyo nokuvezwa.
Ukuguquka kwenza ukwahluka kwezinto zeofuzo ezintsha, kwaye ukhetho luya kususa kwizinto ezibonakalayo.
Ukwahlukana kokwahlukana kunye nokuhlanganiswa kwehla kwenyuke phakathi kwezigaba ezimbli kwisizukulwana ngasinye.
